  "text": "Furthermore, this work can be improved to help to combat against counter-forensic approaches, as presented in [CITATION_1] . Future work includes analyzing some counter-forensic techniques to this work and the application of this technique to other pattern recognition and vision problems as it is general enough and we envision other applications for it. Experiments considering low-quality images can also be performed in a future work.",
